      <title>摩根大通在美联储大幅降息后仍未确定下一步该怎么做</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/jpmorgan-aced-fed-s-big-cut-it-s-less-sure-on-what-comes-next</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根大通是华尔街巨头之一，其经济学家正确预测了美联储周三将利率下调半个百分点，该公司表示，再次大幅降息取决于美国劳动力市场的疲软。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/jpmorgan-aced-fed-s-big-cut-it-s-less-sure-on-what-comes-next</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Sep 2024 09:20:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储首次降息后，交易员转向数据，美国国债上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/treasuries-gain-as-traders-turn-to-data-after-first-fed-cut-done</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易员们对备受期待的降息政策有了新的认识，并将注意力重新集中在劳动力市场的状况上，美国国债小幅上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/treasuries-gain-as-traders-turn-to-data-after-first-fed-cut-done</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Sep 2024 09:14:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
